// freq generation formula: freq = 62500/(2*(1+CMP0)), CMP0 = (31250/freq) - 1, timepassed_ms = 1000/freq = 20*(1+CMP0)/(625)
// this is the waveform generation timer that routes the waveform to PB0, controlling LED blink freq
